        <briefdescription>
<para>Apply the pending changes and return the uncommitted changes for validation. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>This does not result in a permanent update. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>The uncommitted changes that would be committed by calling <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdate_1a4a5df6d83b7a4a3c4dac19a77945be71" kindref="member">Commit()</ref>, or an error:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>ValidationFailed: the pending changes cannot be applied to the current metadata</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>InvalidArgument: if pending changes are conflicting or invalid </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
