        <briefdescription>
<para>Apply the pending changes and commit. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>An OK status if the commit was successful, or an error:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>ValidationFailed: if it cannot be applied to the current table metadata.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>CommitFailed: if it cannot be committed due to conflicts.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>CommitStateUnknown: unknown status, no cleanup should be done. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
