    <briefdescription>
<para>Base class for all kinds of table metadata updates. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Any created <computeroutput><ref refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdate" kindref="compound">PendingUpdate</ref></computeroutput> instance is tracked by the <computeroutput><ref refid="classiceberg_1_1Transaction" kindref="compound">Transaction</ref></computeroutput> instance and commit is also delegated to the <computeroutput><ref refid="classiceberg_1_1Transaction" kindref="compound">Transaction</ref></computeroutput> instance.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Implementations are expected to use builder pattern and errors should be handled by the <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1ErrorCollector" kindref="compound">ErrorCollector</ref> base class. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
